            "description_en": "**🔴 “A fully interactive humanoid robot designed to engage naturally with its surroundings.\n🔴 Powered by an AI system capable of answering any question in real time.\n🔴 Includes a customizable and editable script tailored for essential data handling.\n🔴 Integrated face-tracking sensors for dynamic human–robot interaction.\n🔴 Features mouth-movement simulation synchronized with speech.\n🔴 Equipped with sensors to monitor key vital parameters.\n🔴 Supports seamless control through voice commands.”**",
            "description_ar": "روبوت بشري يقوم بالتفاعل مع من حوله\nAI للرد على اي سؤال\nبه اسكريبت يمكن تعديله مخصص لبيانات اساسية\nفيه سينسورات لتتبع الوجه\nيحاكي حركه الفم اثناء الكلام \nسينسورات لقياس بعض القيم الحيوية\nالتحكم فيه بالاوامر الصوتيه\"",
