            "description_en": "This graduation project focuses on building a smart and secure airport environment using\nadvanced technologies like Artificial Intelligence (AI), Internet of Things (IoT), and network\nsimulation/emulation tools. The system aims to enhance cybersecurity, communication\nsafety, physical infrastructure security, and predictive maintenance through AI-powered\nsolutions.",
