            "description_en": "Due to the deteriorating conditions in the Mediterranean recently, one of the major causes of its destruction has been single-use plastic, which takes millions of years to decompose. In this project, I will study the components of plastic that make it non-biodegradable and replace them with simpler, biodegradable materials.",
